OpenOCD Strong Points a.k.a. Why I Continue to Use OpenOCD

* Established community focal point for new CPU and microcontroller support
As new hardware comes out:
	* chip clock setup
	* chip miscallaneous setupdetails, e.g. interrupt vector relocation, boot to isp mode etc
	* chip flash algorithms
	* debug adapters

* Search for OpenOCD in https://plus.google.com/+AndreyYurovsky/posts
